ecause you\'re a TotalGuard Yard Care customer.<br><a href="https://tgyardcare.com/unsubscribe" style="color:#999999; text-decoration:underline;">Unsubscribe</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://tgyardcare.com/email-preferences" style="color:#999999; text-decoration:underline;">Email Preferences</a></p></td></tr></table></td></tr>';
