    subheadline: '16 days left for double referral rewards. The math is hard to ignore.',
    bodyHtml: '<p>Hey {{first_name}},</p><p>We\u2019re at the halfway point of our Midsummer Referral Blitz, and the results have been amazing \u2014 dozens of new customers signed up this month because people like you spread the word.</p><p><strong>But there\u2019s still 16 days left, and we want to make sure you don\u2019t miss out.</strong></p><h3>Quick Recap</h3><ul><li>You refer someone \u2192 <strong>$50 off your next service</strong></li><li>They book \u2192 <strong>$50 off their first service</strong></li><li>No limit \u2192 <strong>Refer everyone you know</strong></li></ul><h3>The Simple Math</h3><p>Think about your street. Your cul-de-sac. Your coworkers who complain about their lawn guy. Your friend who\u2019s been doing it themselves and hates every minute of it.</p><p><strong>Refer 3 people this month = $150 in savings for you.</strong></p><p>That\u2019s real money off real services. Some customers have already referred 4-5 people this month. One customer in Sun Prairie referred 7 neighbors and has enough credit to cover their next two mowing visits.</p><h3>Not Sure What to Say?</h3><p>Just forward this email. Or text them this:</p><blockquote style="background:#f5f5f5; padding:16px; border-left:4px solid #2d6a2e; border-radius:4px;"><p><em>\"My yard care company is running a deal \u2014 $50 off your first service if you sign up in July. They\u2019re called TotalGuard and they\u2019re legit. Same crew every time, great communication. (608) 535-6057 or tgyardcare.com \u2014 just mention my name.\"</em></p></blockquote><p>16 days. $50 per referral. No limit. Go.</p>',
